Episk digt med 17 illustrationer i qadjarisk stil. Handler om digterinden Rābi'ah, der levede midt i 900-tallet, nu kvindelig nationalhelt i Afganistan.

Epic poetry with 17 illustrations in qadjarisk style. The work is about the female poet Rābi'ah, from the middle of the 10th Century, now a national female hero in Afganistan.
Litography from Tabrīz 1270 H (1891 CE).
